room_title: Escape room "The Penitentiary" by Omescape in San Francisco
room_description: You wake up in a dark cell. You can't remember how you got here, but you quickly realize you must find a way to escape. You have heard the rumors about the Night Stalker, one of the most infamous serial killers in American history, and his twisted mind games. Several incidents reported strange disappearances from his prison cell. Will you be the next victim? You have an hour to escape your fate!
